==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solidness
<hw>Sol"id*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>State or quality of
being solid; firmness; compactness; solidity, as of material
bodies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Soundness; strength; truth; validity, as of
arguments, reasons, principles, and the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Solidungula</ent>⟦br⟧
\'d8
